    "The parameter is set to conspiracy_with_ai. model",
    "The parameter specifies one of the models defined in the Simple Chat configuration.",
    "When models are used as experimental conditions, this value can be defined as a variable and passed through the Qualtrics survey flow experiment_id",
    "The parameter indicates the treatment condition assigned to the participant. participant_id",
    "The parameter serves as a unique identifier for the task and makes it possible to match user data from Qualtrics or other platforms with the data recorded in Simple Chat."
